articles.title: Most of America missed the start of Eagles-Chiefs, even Sunday Ticket subscribers - NBC Sports
articles.description: As Fox stayed with Giants-Cowboys overtime, the Eagles-Chiefs Super Bowl rematch couldn't be seen by most viewers.
articles.content: When the NFL released the 2025 schedule, one of the most-anticipated games was the Super Bowl rematch between the Eagles and Chiefs. But when kickoff came, hardly anyone in America was able to watch.… [+1240 chars]
